Package org.sd.extract

Interface Summary
ExtractionData Container interface for various types of extraction data.
Extractor A "mini extractor" to apply to a doc text.
Interpretation Container for an interpretation of an extraction.
InterpretationChooser Interface for choosing an interpretation for each extraction in an extraction group's extractions.
Interpreter Interface for interpreting an extraction.
TagNodeAcceptor Interface for accepting a node with an extracted tag.
TextAcceptor Interface for determining whether to accept doc text for further processing.
TextContainer Caching iterator iterface around a text document tunable for memory and performance, particulary with potentially massive text documents.
TextSplitter Interface for splitting text to extract from.
WordAcceptor Interface for accepting a word.
 

Class Summary
AbstractBaseExtractor An abstract base extractor implementation.
AbstractEntityExtractor An abstract extractor implementation for extracting entities.
AbstractExtractionData Abstract extraction data implementation.
AbstractExtractor Abstract implementation of the Extractor interface.
AbstractExtractorFSM Abstract implementation of the Extractor interface using a Finite State Machine (FSM) parser.
AbstractTextNodeExtractor An abstract extractor that operates on every text node in each docText.
AllLinksAcceptor A link acceptor that accepts every link.
BaseTextContainer<T> Base implementation of the text container interface.
BaseWordAcceptor Base implementation for the WordAcceptor interface.
Bite Container for a portion (or "bite") of a post.
BlogSnippetExtractor Utility to extract blog snippets.
BlogSnippetGroup Container for extraction group(s) for blog snippets.
DefaultInterpretation A default implementation of the interpretation interface.
DefaultInterpreter Default interpreter for the DefaultInterpretation.
Disambiguator Utility to resolve ambiguities within extraction groups.
DocText Container for text from a document as served through a text container.
DocumentOrderExtractionComparator A comparator for sorting extractions into document order.
DomainLinkAcceptor A link acceptor that accepts links to domain roots.
Extraction Container for extraction information for a DocText.
ExtractionGroup Container for extractions with the same path key.
ExtractionHarness Utility to run extractors.
ExtractionMatcherData Extraction data for holding a matcher from a regex pattern.
ExtractionParseData Extraction data for holding parses.
ExtractionPipeline A "mega extractor" to apply multiple regular extractors to a document (text container).
ExtractionProperties Container for extraction properties.
ExtractionResults Container for extraction results from a document.
ExtractionRunner Wrapper class for running a pipeline.
ExtractionSnippet Container class for an extraction-based snippet.
ExtractionStringData Extraction data for holding a string.
ExtractionStringsData Extraction data for holding a list of strings.
ExtractionUtil Extraction utilities.
ExtractionXmlData Container for extracted xml data.
FirstInterpretationDisambiguator A disambiguator that always chooses the first interpretation.
HasWordExtractor An extractor to recognize text nodes that contain one of a set of (already normalized) words.
HeadingExtractor An extractor for html headings.
HeadingOrganizer Utility class to organize extracted headings and relate them to text.
HeadingOrganizer.HeadingStack Container class to hold a stack of headings.
HeadingOrganizer.IndexHeadingStack Container class to hold a stack of headings with their range of influence.
HeadingOrganizer.KeyHeadingStack Heading stack for key headings including the key headings' index headings.
LinkExtractor A hyperlink extractor.
LiteralExtractor An extractor to recognize literal (normalized) strings.
PivotContextExtractor An extractor to pull contextual strings from a document surrounding (before) pivot extractions.
Post Container for holding snippet posts.
RegexAcceptor A regex-based text acceptor.
RegexExtractor A simple regex extractor.
RegexSplitter A regex-based text splitter.
RelativeLinksAcceptor A link acceptor that accepts only relative links.
SingleLineTextContainer A text container that holds a single line.
SnippetExtractor Class for extracting snippets from a document.
StopwordsBasedAcceptor A word acceptor that accepts all but stopwords.
TagExtractor An arbitrary tag extractor.
TextFileExtractionPipeline An extraction pipeline operating over text files.
TextFileTextContainer Implementation of a text container for text file lines.
WordsExtractor A simple extractor that just grabs words from text.
XmlExtractionPipeline An extraction pipeline operating over xml files.
XmlTextContainer Implementation of a text container for xml (or html) data.
